OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1771878199
OL,3,CInvestigations launched into online
OL,4,Cracial abuse of football players
OL,6,FThe UK Football Police Unit (UKFPU)
OL,7,Fhas launched a number of
OL,8,Finvestigations following reports of
OL,9,Fonline racial abuse against Premier
OL,10,FLeague footballers.
OL,12,FThe UKFPU said on Monday that it
OL,13,Freceived four separate reports of
OL,14,Fonline racial abuse in the last three
OL,15,Fdays.
OL,17,FIt added that it would be "working
OL,18,Fclosely with all the football clubs
OL,19,Fand their players to help identify the
OL,20,Fpeople responsible".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1771878199
OL,3,CInvestigations launched into online
OL,4,Cracial abuse of football players
OL,6,FWhile the UKFPU did not name any
OL,7,Fplayers involved in the
OL,8,Finvestigations, several football clubs
OL,9,Freleased statements condemning racial
OL,10,Fabuse in relation to their players
OL,11,Fover the weekend.
OL,13,FWolverhampton Wolves on Sunday wrote
OL,14,Fthat the club was "disgusted by
OL,15,Fnumerous instances of racist abuse,
OL,16,Ffrom multiple perpetrators, directed
OL,17,Fat Tolu Arokodare on social media
OL,18,Ffollowing (Sunday's) fixture against
OL,19,FCrystal Palace".
OL,26,@zD@KpmzD@Tpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1771878199
OL,3,CInvestigations launched into online
OL,4,Cracial abuse of football players
OL,6,F"Tolu has our full and unwavering
OL,7,Fsupport. No player should be subjected
OL,8,Fto such hatred simply for doing their
OL,9,Fjob. We stand firmly alongside him,
OL,10,Fand alongside all footballers who are
OL,11,Fforced to endure this abuse from
OL,12,Fanonymous accounts acting with
OL,13,Fapparent impunity."
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
