CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1771878199
OL,3,CInvestigations launched into online
OL,4,Cracial abuse of football players
OL,6,FThe club included screenshots of some
OL,7,Fof the comments targeting Arokodare,
OL,8,Fwho is from Nigeria.
OL,10,FArokodare posted examples of some of
OL,11,Fthe racist comments he had been
OL,12,Freceiving on social media, alongside a
OL,13,Fstatement that said: "It's still
OL,14,Funbelievable to me that we're playing
OL,15,Fin a time where people have so much
OL,16,Ffreedom to communicate such racism
OL,17,Fwithout any consequences."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
