CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1771878199
OL,3,CInvestigations launched into online
OL,4,Cracial abuse of football players
OL,6,FSunderland AFC similarly posted a
OL,7,Fstatement on its website on Sunday,
OL,8,Fsaying it was "appalled by the vile
OL,9,Fonline racist abuse directed at
OL,10,FRomaine Mundle following (Sunday's)
OL,11,FPremier League fixture against Fulham".
OL,13,F"The abhorrent behaviour displayed by
OL,14,Fmultiple individuals is unacceptable
OL,15,Fand will not be tolerated by the Club
OL,16,Funder any circumstances," the
OL,17,Fstatement said.
OL,26,@rD@ZpmrD@cpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1771878199
OL,3,CInvestigations launched into online
OL,4,Cracial abuse of football players
OL,6,F"There is no place for racism in our
OL,7,Fsociety, and we stand with Romaine,
OL,8,Fwho has our full support. The Club is
OL,9,Factively working with the relevant
OL,10,Fauthorities and online platforms to
OL,11,Fidentify those responsible, and we
OL,12,Fwill take the strongest possible
OL,13,Faction available to us."
OL,15,FBurnley FC wrote that it was
OL,16,F"disgusted" by online racial abuse
OL,17,Fdirected at Hannibal Mejbri following
OL,18,FSaturday's Premier League fixture.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1771878199
OL,3,CInvestigations launched into online
OL,4,Cracial abuse of football players
OL,6,F"The Club continues to be unequivocal
OL,7,Fin its stance - we have a zero-
OL,8,Ftolerance approach to any form of
OL,9,Fdiscrimination.
OL,11,F"The Club has reported the post to
OL,12,FInstagram's parent company, Meta, and
OL,13,Fexpects strong support from them,
OL,14,Ftogether with the Premier League and
OL,15,Fthe Police, and will work to ensure
OL,16,Fthat the individual responsible is
OL,17,Fidentified and investigated."
OL,19,FWhile Chelsea FC said the racist abuse
OL,20,Fdirected at Wesley Fofana on Saturday
OL,21,Fwas "abhorrent".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1771878199
OL,3,CInvestigations launched into online
OL,4,Cracial abuse of football players
OL,6,F"We stand unequivocally with Wes. He
OL,7,Fhas our full support, as do all our
OL,8,Fplayers who are too often forced to
OL,9,Fendure this hatred simply for doing
OL,10,Ftheir job. We will work with the
OL,11,Frelevant authorities and platforms in
OL,12,Fidentifying the perpetrators and take
OL,13,Fthe strongest possible action."
OL,15,FThe UKFPU said that it has seen a
OL,16,Fnumber of successful prosecutions for
OL,17,Fonline racial abuse in recent months,
OL,18,Fbut recognised that "there is always
OL,19,Fmore to do".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1771878199
OL,3,CInvestigations launched into online
OL,4,Cracial abuse of football players
OL,6,F"There is absolutely no place for
OL,7,Fracial abuse, either online or in
OL,8,Fperson, and anyone who believes they
OL,9,Fcan hide behind their keyboards should
OL,10,Fthink again," UKFPU head Chief
OL,11,FConstable Mark Roberts said on Monday.
OL,13,F"The UKFPU condemns this abhorrent
OL,14,Fbehaviour and we will ensure that,
OL,15,Fthrough our dedicated team of
OL,16,Fofficers, we do everything possible to
OL,17,Fidentify those responsible and bring
OL,18,Fthem to justice."
OL,26,@uD@AOUzD@QO]
